🚨 OpenClaw (ex-Clawdbot/Moltbot): Viral open-source AI agent for local messaging, files & shell cmds—but rapid 2026 adoption raises alarms over
severe compromise risks! 🔒

Below is KQL to detect the pressence in your org.

DeviceFileEvents
| where Timestamp > ago(30d)
| where FileName has_any ("moltbot.json", "clawd.json", "clawbot.json")
 or FolderPath has_any ("/.clawdbot/", "/.moltbot/", "/.openclaw/")
| project Timestamp, DeviceName, ActionType, FileName, FolderPath, InitiatingProcessCommandLine
| union (
 DeviceProcessEvents
 | where Timestamp > ago(7d)
 | where ProcessCommandLine has_any ("clawd", "moltbot", "openclaw")
 | project Timestamp, DeviceName, ActionType, FileName, FolderPath, ProcessCommandLine, AccountName
)
